      "title": "Operation",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "This is a simple workflow for single image captioning using an LLM backend server.\n\n1. Type/paste in your user prompt & system prompt manually, or connect the user/system prompt nodes to load presets from the node directories.\n\n2. Set the server URL\n3. Select your local model\n4. Adjust parameters [Overrides backend settings on each pass]\n5. Toggle 'Unload all models' on/off for memory management between passes [This is good for unloading your LLM if you use this as part of a more complex image generation workflow]\n6. Connect any/all of my Display nodes to see your desired outputs.\n\nLove & digital kisses\nApolonia 💜\n\n"
      ],
      "color": "#9414ff",
